            <div class="col s12 m7">
                <div class="card small">
                    <div class="card-image">
                        <img src="~/images/PF/UR_board.jpg" class="materialboxed" />
                        <span class="card-title">User research</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <span>
                            These are the things that the userswant to be able todo.
                        </span>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col s12 m5">
                <div class="card-panel teal">
                    <span class="white-text">
                        These 'things'are collected by the user researchers (UR's) and roughly grouped together to create bodies of work.
                    </span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-footer">
        <a href="#!" class="modal-close waves-effect waves-green btn-flat">close</a>
    </div>
</div>
